Despite uncertainty that still exists given the risks to the banking system and the rise of recent
geopolitical tensions and conflicts, ACRES is well positioned through its 100% floating rate loan
portfolio to drive meaningful returns and to take advantage of the market dislocation.
Additionally, our proactive asset management approach to investing continues to be an asset in
these turbulent market conditions.

Our mission remains to deliver to you, ACR’s shareholders, value over the long term. We remain
focused on maximizing earnings and growing book value by investing in high-quality assets and
strategically returning capital through share repurchases and ultimately dividends over time.

We are grateful to the whole ACRES team for their efforts and success in 2022, and to you for
